<emphasis id="B0918D5C949ED9601B01B5A3ABA18D47" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Figure 6.</emphasis>
Stream in primary forest of Gunung Mulu National Park, Sarawak, type locality of 
<taxonomicName id="4A7A9CEF95BE10DEC15296AD64EB0840" authorityName="Kodada &amp; Jäch &amp; Selnekovič &amp; Goffová" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Elmidae" genus="Okalia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Okalia necopinata" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="79" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="necopinata">
